This is a simple play template for building RESTful web services
 . You can use this template for your projects too
 . Don't forget to contribute ;)

- Project
 . Use JDK 8
 . Scala version is 2.11.8 (You can change it in build.sbt)
 . SBT version is 0.13.11 (You can change it build.properties)

- Test
 . Write test for all your controllers and services, trust me, this is very helpful :)

- Dependencies
 . jBCrypt, is an implementation the OpenBSD Blowfish password hashing algorithm
 . HashIDs, small Scala library to generate YouTube-like hashes from one or many numbers
 . Reactivemongo, Async and Non-blocking scala driver for MongoDB

